snippet.title: Jeff Foster Official
snippet.description:
With humour and much compassion, Jeff Foster speaks simply and directly about nonduality, spiritual awakening… and the extraordinary sacredness of life’s ordinary moments.
Website: http://www.lifewithoutacentre.com/
Sign up to Jeff's free newsletter: http://tiny.cc/jefffoster
